dct_title_s: Road map of Mercer County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Panel title: Map of Mercer County, New Jersey : showing principal highway routes. "Prepared for public distribution by the Mercer County Board of Chosen Freeholders"--Panel. Text, ill., "List of roads under jurisdiction of the Board of Freeholders, Mercer County, N.J.," which also serves as index, on verso.
dct_publisher_sm: [Trenton, N.J.] : Mercer County Board of Chosen Freeholders, 1930.
